data.description: Gorgeous move-in ready single-family home Family-friendly neighborhood! Large fenced yard perfect for the whole family.Walking distance to parks & an elementary school. Recent updates include new impact windows that provide ample natural light & makes the home more energy efficient, porcelain floors throughout. Open concept & large floorplan makes this home great for entertaining. The kitchen has clean lines, beautiful granite counters & Honey maple soft close cabinets & drawers. GE smudge proof S/S appliances are a dream. Large master w/ his & her closets & updated bathrm. laundry room & 2 car garage. Enjoy the custom backyard w/ its one of a kind patio perfect for hosting BBQ. No Rear Neighbors!!!A/C 2022! Water Haater 2022!
